Guy Wilson (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Guy_Wilson_(actor) 0 Guy Allan Wilson Jr. (born November 21, 1985) is an American actor, known for his roles in such television series as NCIS, Castle, Bones, and Breaking Bad, as well the feature film Werewolf: The Beast Among Us. He portrayed Will Horton on the daytime soap opera Days of Our Lives from 2014 to 2015.
